Title: Get the Sheriff!
Description: A rape case opens racial divisions in a small town. A black sheriff and his white deputy investigate allegations that a wealthy white businessman raped a black college student.
Short Description: A racial tensions flare as a Black sheriff investigates a small town rape case.

Title: Brother from Another Planet:the animated feature
Description: A mute alien with the appearance of a black human is chased by outer-space bounty hunters through the streets of Harlem.
Short Description: An alien in a Black body is chased by space bounty hunters.
